        Great marketing knowledge and awesome customer service. Adam helped me set up my business and jumpstart my lead generation strategy. He's truly your guy if you're looking to grow. *paraphrased
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900">
        Chad <span class="font-bold">W.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
      <div class="gap-1 mb-6">
        <Stars />
